snippet.title: Anonymously Leaked Video Proves Amber Heard Attacked her Sister, Says Johnny Depp's Lawyers
snippet.description:
JOHNNY DEPP: #JohnnyDepp's lawyer played a video in court that they say proves #AmberHeard attacked her sister. The video was anonymously leaked to Depp's legal team. Should this affect his libel case?

Watch #CourtTV LIVE tonight at 8/7c. court.tv/live
